la.), January 27, 1900", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn83016194/1900-01-27/ed-1/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn90052143/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn90052143"], "batch": ["gu_javert_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1906", "description": ["Daily (Saturday and Sunday issues combined), <Feb. 16/17, 2008-> Began with Sept. 30, 1906 issue?; ceased with vol. 114, no. 300 (Aug. 31, 2016). Some issues may lack statement of publisher. Other issues may occasionally be combined. Occasional irregularities or errors in enumeration and chronology. Some enumeration or chronology repeated in error. Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Description based on: Vol. 6, no. 8 (Oct. 2, 1906). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 114, no. 300 (Aug. 31, 2016). News (Brunswick, Ga.) (DLC) 2016233534 (OCoLC)960210036"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.942Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-09", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-09"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn90052143/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [31.168992, -81.50248], "location": ["georgia", "glynn county", "glynn", "brunswick", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-81.50248, 31.168992], "number": ["microfilm master", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "sn90052142", "sn90052143", "1", "21707708", "2016233534", "3138", "online resource", "1090-3895", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn90052143/1922-12-25/ed-1/", "2024-05-12t17:32:27.269094", "univ of georgia", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn90052143/1906-10-02/ed-1/", "microfilm service copy", "2020-08-13t16:48:57"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Published September 8-12, 1908; <September 22, 1908>-July 16, 1909 with title: Brunswick daily news", "Brunswick daily news"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "catalog", "serial and government publications division", "the brunswick news (brunswick, ga.;[brunswick, georgia?]) 1906-2016", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 82.55833, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn90052143", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["georgia", "brunswick (ga.)", "glynn county", "newspapers", "glynn", "brunswick", "glynn county (ga.)", "electronic journals", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-22T07:56:54.836Z", "title": "The Brunswick news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn90052143/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271078/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "188?", "dates": ["[1880 TO 1900]"], "description": ["Daily (except Monday) Ceased with volume 11, number 196 (August 15, 1900). Some irregularities in enumeration. Some issues may not carry enumeration. Some enumeration may be repeated numerous times in error. No issue published for July 5, 1899. Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries. Published also as a weekly ed. (title unknown). Merged with: Evening call (Brunswick, Ga.), to form: Brunswick times-call. Cannot determine relationship to: Brunswick times-advertiser, which appeared for an undetermined amount of time in the 1800s from the same publisher. Description based on: April 25, 1889; title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 13, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Volume 11, Number 196 (August 15, 1900) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 13, 2020). Evening call (Brunswick, Ga.) Brunswick times-call (OCoLC)1145169362"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:51.196Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271078/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["georgia", "glynn county", "glynn", "brunswick", "united states"], "number": ["2026-04-13t21:30:13", "2020271078", "2693-5252", "online resource", "1145169764"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Daily times", "May sometimes be known also as: Morning times"], "partof": ["the brunswick times (brunswick, ga.;brunswick, ga;c. w. deming) 188?-1900 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 73.27921, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["georgia", "brunswick (ga.)", "glynn county", "newspapers", "glynn", "brunswick", "journaux", "glynn county (ga.)", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:00:49.563Z", "title": "The Brunswick times", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2020271078/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271079/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1901", "dates": ["[1901 TO 1903]"], "description": ["Daily (except Monday) Began in 1901; ceased with volume 2, number 189 (May 7, 1903). Stated frequency is daily; actual frequency appears to be daily except Monday. Occasional errors in enumeration and chronology. Some enumeration repeated in error. Numerous issues from volume 2 called volume 1 in error. Also on microfilm: Athens, Ga. : University of Georgia Libraries. Description based on: Volume 1, Number 92 (January 11, 1902); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 13, 2020). Latest issue consulted: Volume 2, Number 189 (May 7, 1903) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed August 13, 2020). Brunswick daily news (OCoLC)1145169621"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:51.196Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2020271079/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["georgia", "glynn coun