ughout Use South and there is no question but that Col Kingman will have their unanimous endorsement at the prop er time as recognition in part of his work and efforts on behalf of the South during his many years service in this section Never has this portion of the coun try had"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T12:58:36.033Z", "group": ["ndnp/gu", "digital-library-of-georgia-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn90052143/1913-06-21/ed-1/?sp=1", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_lassiter_ver01:data:sn90052143:00414182719:1913062101:0455/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=419&w=335", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_lassiter_ver01:data:sn90052143:00414182719:1913062101:0455/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=838&w=671", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/gu/batch_gu_lassiter_ver01/data/sn90052143/00414182719/1913062101/0455.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["georgia", "glynn county", "glynn", "brunswick", "united states"], "location_city": ["brunswick"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["glynn"], "location_state": ["georgia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["4", "1", "0", "8", "9", "7", "sn90052143", "2", "0000000001"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["sn90052143"], "number_page": ["0000000001"], "number_reel": ["0", "0", "4", "1", "4", "1", "8", "2", "7", "1", "9"], "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Published September 8-12, 1908; <September 22, 1908>-July 16, 1909 with title: Brunswick daily news"], "partof": ["chronicling america", "the brunswick news (brunswick, ga.;[brunswick, georgia?]) 1906-2016", "serial and government publications division"], "partof_c